<h1 align="center">The Verge</h1>
<h2>About the game</h2>
The game was conceived during "Pelit ja Mobiilit" course in Metropolia in spring 2018. 
<h2>Game requirements</h2>
The game requires:
<ul>
<li>Python3 interpreter</li>
<li>Internet connection</li>
<li>Patience</li>
</ul>
<h2>Game Influences</h2>	
As far as we know ourselves, this is what influenced the game:
<ul>
<li>Outlast</li>
<li>Shutter Island (2010)</li>
<li>Dark Souls</li>
<li>Silent Hill</li>
</ul>	

